123
00:07:39,414 --> 00:07:40,784
<font size='34'>හ්ම්ම්?</font>

124
00:07:41,304 --> 00:07:42,284
<font size='34'>ඒයි...</font>

125
00:07:42,284 --> 00:07:44,124
<font size='34'>ඒයි!</font>

126
00:07:44,124 --> 00:07:45,414
<font size='34'>ඇයි?</font>

127
00:07:45,414 --> 00:07:46,734
